Deal Insights

Deal insights help you answer questions such as how is the deal progressing? What milestones have been met? What interactions are planned for the future?

Use the Deal Insights Dashboard

Click fields on the left to populate charts on the right. Click Total $ Received Fee to understand what is your deal profitability status. Click # Call Reports to understand overall client engagement, and what interactions you plan to engage with the customer.

KPI Calculations -Total Received Fee
Received Fee: Sum of Received Fee for the Account.
Received Fee Donut: Received Fee/ TotalExpectedFee for the Account.

KPI Calculations - # Call Reports
# Call Reports: Count of call reports(Interaction Summary object) created in YTD.
Call Report Breakdown: Count of call reports by InteractionType.

KPI Calculations - Days Since Last Interaction
Days Since Last Interaction: Days between Last Interaction (StartTime) until now for that Deal.
title: Deal Insights in CRM Analytics
